id: pm-ts-starter-yybv
title: Harden release bun-verify so registry-mirror lag cannot block the GitHub release
description: Make the Daily Release resilient to bun registry-mirror lag so a cosmetic verify failure never blocks the actual GitHub release.
type: Chore
status: closed
priority: 1
tags[2]: ci,release-readiness
created_at: "2026-06-13T22:29:39.877Z"
updated_at: "2026-07-18T09:59:48.622Z"
deadline: "2026-06-15T00:00:00.000Z"
closed_at: "2026-07-18T09:59:48.619Z"
author: claude
estimated_minutes: 30
acceptance_criteria: "bun-verify retries 8x then falls back to authoritative 'npm view pkg@version'; npm-confirmed publishes emit ::warning:: and exit 0 so Create GitHub release runs; only a genuinely-absent npm version fails the job; CI green; no secrets."
resolution: release.yml verify step falls back to authoritative npm view after bun-verify retries
expected_result: bun-verify never blocks the GitHub release on registry-mirror lag
actual_result: Fallback shipped fleet-wide 2026-06-14; Daily Releases green since (verified 2026-07-18)
comments[2]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-13T22:29:39.877Z",claude,Identical release.yml verify block across all active pm repos; same deterministic transform applied.
  "2026-07-18T09:59:47.931Z",pi-agent,"Verified done 2026-07-18: .github/workflows/release.yml contains the npm-authoritative fallback (npm view fallback after bun-verify retries), shipped fleet-wide 2026-06-14; multiple successful Daily Releases since (latest July 2026). Acceptance criteria met."
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-13T22:29:39.877Z",claude,See pm-changelog PR #49 for the lead fix and full rationale.
learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-13T22:29:39.877Z",claude,"Calendar -N suffixes are semver prereleases; bun resolves them via a registry mirror that lags npm publish,making the verify smoke test the flakiest for -N releases."
files[1]{path,scope,note}:
  .github/workflows/release.yml,project,verify step npm-authoritative fallback
tests[1]{command,scope,timeout_seconds}:
  bun --version,project,60
docs[1]{path,scope,note}:
  .github/workflows/release.yml,project,release workflow being hardened
close_reason: npm-authoritative bun-verify fallback shipped; acceptance criteria met
body: "The 'Verify bun install of published package' step was fatal (5x30s then exit 1) and ordered before 'Create GitHub release', so bun registry-mirror lag (worst for prerelease -N versions) could block the real release after npm publish + tag + changelog commit already succeeded. This actually blocked pm-changelog 2026.6.13-1's GitHub release. Fleet-wide propagation of the pm-changelog#49 fix (npm-authoritative fallback)."
